  m_Name: InstrumentSO_Cornu_de_Pompeii
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  instrumentName: Cornu de Pompeii
  description: "Cornu de Pompeii l\xE0 m\u1ED9t lo\u1EA1i k\xE8n \u0111\u1ED3ng c\u1ED5
    \u0111\u1EA1i c\u1EE7a La M\xE3, c\xF3 h\xECnh d\xE1ng cong h\xECnh ch\u1EEF
    G, d\xE0i kho\u1EA3ng 3 m\xE9t. Nh\u1EA1c c\u1EE5 n\xE0y th\u01B0\u1EDDng \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
    d\xF9ng trong qu\xE2n \u0111\u1ED9i La M\xE3 c\u1ED5 \u0111\u1EA1i \u0111\u1EC3
    ra hi\u1EC7u l\u1EC7nh, c\u0169ng nh\u01B0 trong c\xE1c nghi l\u1EC5 v\xE0 tr\xECnh
    di\u1EC5n c\xF4ng c\u1ED9ng. \xC2m thanh c\u1EE7a cornu vang d\u1ED9i, m\u1EA1nh
    m\u1EBD, gi\xFAp truy\u1EC1n l\u1EC7nh tr\xEAn chi\u1EBFn tr\u01B0\u1EDDng ho\u1EB7c
    thu h\xFAt s\u1EF1 ch\xFA \xFD trong \u0111\xE1m \u0111\xF4ng. M\u1ED9t s\u1ED1
    m\u1EABu Cornu \u0111\xE3 \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c t\xECm th\u1EA5y t\u1EA1i Pompeii,
    nh\u1EDD \u0111\xF3 c\xF3 th\xEAm b\u1EB1ng ch\u1EE9ng v\u1EC1 vai tr\xF2 quan
    tr\u1ECDng c\u1EE7a nh\u1EA1c c\u1EE5 n\xE0y trong \u0111\u1EDDi s\u1ED1ng La
    M\xE3 c\u1ED5."
